Description:
As you go further into the cave you come across the skeleton of an adventurer, next to him you see a narrow gap in the wall.

It seems that the adventurer tried to cross the gap but it took too long and was swarmed by spiders.

Upon inspecting the gap, you notice a current of air going through it, so it surely leads somewhere else inside the cave.
DescriptionAction: With spiders lurking, you must decide what to do.
